the sky was clear and sunny over much of the nation saturday 
with only widely scattered precipitation 
at midday showers were scattered from central arizona into 
southern nevada over northwestern montana and western south 
dakota and across florida and eastern georgia 
elsewhere showers and thunderstorms developed over new england 
