niche in rural america 
this is my way of counting very quietly i can make a 
difference by the jobs for women by responsible agriculture 
said shaw who lives in a comfortably cluttered farm house 
surrounded by farm fields in my own small way ive come full 
circle rather than thinking that i have to go out and protest 
ive chosen to come back to the country and work 
