divorce and after hearing an inspirational speech by texas 
agriculture commissioner jim hightower 
hightowers talk was about how he was trying to turn around 
the texas food economy by not shipping all of their produce out to 
be processed but instead doing it in state his talk was the basis 
for my doing something like that she said 
