no one wants to get out there and be aggressive they can stay 
on the sidelines and generate some pretty nice yields without much 
risk he said 
gene jay seagle director of technical research at the brokerage 
gruntal financial inc said he thinks the slow trading indicates 
a market that seems to feel the worst that can hit us has 
happened 
this is a very sold out market he said there is so much 
pessimism and so much cash that the chance is for a breakout on 
the upside 
